A '''Team Prime''' was the leader of a squad of [[Mistryl Shadow Guard]] warrior-women. In [[0 BBY/Legends|0 BBY]], for example, [[Manda D'ulin]] was the Team Prime of a group of six warriors, capable of operating as commandos or infiltrators, and also able to perform low-level space missions with their two heavy fighters, the ''[[Skyclaw]]'' and [[Mirage (starship)|''Mirage'']].

Another warrior was the Team Prime of a group of warriors and slicers at the [[Mistryl Safehouse|Mistryl safe house]] on [[Naboo/Legends|Naboo]]<ref name="SWG:CE">{{SWGcite|exp=NGE|type=general|Cam'doen's Enforcer|Naboo}}</ref> in [[1 ABY/Legends|1 ABY]].<ref name="SWG_timeline">{{SWG_timeline}}</ref>

